title: Week 14 Recap, Wentz Hurt, Browns Blow It (Football 12/11)
description:
Will Brinson, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora bring you a Week 14 recap from across the NFL! First, Will, Nick and Pete discuss the potentially devastating injury to Eagles QB Carson Wentz and if Philly has a chance without him. Then, the guys recap Panthers-Vikings before analyzing the NFC playoff picture and who has the best chance to reach the Super Bowl, before hitting on the AFC race. Then, JLC joins Will to break down another impressive effort from Jimmy G, Baker Mayfield's stop at the CBS Studios in New York, bad coaching in Cleveland, Cincy, and Tampa Bay, before reacting to the wild snow game in Buffalo.
